  "original_title": "\u0dad\u0dd9\u0dbd\u0dca \u0db4\u0ddd\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dda \u0db6\u0dd9\u0daf\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dcf \u0d9a\u0dd4\u0da9\u0dd4 \u0dc3\u0db8\u0d9c 03\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db8\u0dcf\u0da7\u0dca\u0da7\u0dd4",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "03 were caught with the powder brought to distribute in the oil queue",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Ambalanthota police said that a woman and two youths were arrested yesterday evening (05th) along with 15 grams and 300 milligrams of intoxicating powder which were brought to be distributed to young people in the oil queues in and around Ambalantota city.",
        "Mr. Jagath Wijegunaratne, Head of Police, Ambalanthota, said that investigations have revealed that information has been received that the drug trafficker, who is currently in prison for drug offences, is using his mistress to conduct the traffic.",
        "Ambalantota Police say that they were able to trap these drug dealers during the investigations conducted on the basis of information received by the Ambalantota Police that the bag containing drug powder which was hidden near an electric ditch on the Ambalantota Nonagama Ambilipitiya road was taken from that place.",
        "The police say that the two youths were arrested with the drugs and the woman who led them was also arrested after receiving information that the drugs were taken to the house of the drug trafficker's mistress who is currently in prison in Ambalantota Waragodella area and given to the traffickers to sell them.",
        "8 grams and 50 milligrams of drug powder were found in the pants pocket of this 32-year-old woman. The police said that a 31-year-old youth resident of Ambalantota Waragodella with 5 grams and 100 milligrams of thibu drug for distribution was arrested and a 20-year-old youth resident of Gamaralagama with 2 grams and 150 milligram of drug powder was arrested.",
        "The police have arrested the woman who had two small electronic scales for measuring the drugs very carefully for retail sale."
      ],
